'''Tecave''' was a grass that grew only on the planet [[Cerea/Legends|Cerea]]. Tecave was important to the inhabitants because is was used in the production of [[Guilea/Legends|guilea]]. It was also in high demand off-planet. However, it could not survive without [[malium]] in the atmosphere, a substance rare on most worlds but plentiful on Cerea.

